descript.abstract: This data set, cntyphysical, consists of a single polygon for Hillsborough County. Along land boundaries with other counties it matches the outline of parcels. The coastline boundaries were verified utilizing aerial photography and other resources.
descript.purpose: This data set is intended to show the Hillsborough County boundaries as they are designated by natural features in combination and legal description.
